*   ## **_The Vision def. The Usos_**
    
    ## **_Special Guest Ref: LA Knight_**
    

The match was essentially no DQ match as LA Knight did not enforce any rules. Tables, Chairs, steps and more.

The match ends when Bron hits a double spear on the Usos and Bronson hits a Tsunami

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/e644dfe2-05b5-4996-a23b-5df5d4b93d03/17693.jpg)

Michael Cole confirmed that the Crown Jewel Championships will be defended at the Crown Jewel PLE in Australia.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/a98ff46b-bc25-48ed-9256-cd7af93931af/17706.jpg)

*   ## **_WWE WOMEN'S CHAMPIONSHIP: STEPHANIE VAQUER DEF. IYO SKY_**
    

Stephanie Vaquer is THE NEW WWE Women Champion!

What a moment!! What a match!!!

Stephanie wins with a modified Spiral Tap

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/dbd7c7a5-88ca-4e9b-bd10-26815afecd84/17711.jpg)

Tears from Stephanie Vaquer after an incredible performance in front of her father.

Tears from her father as she presents him her World Championship.

What an incredible moment and match all around.

