*   ## **_CM Punk and AJ Lee def. Seth Rollins and Becky Lynch_**
    

Very fun match that saw both couples using each other's moves. AJ Lee taps out Becky Lynch for the win.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/c13118a2-448d-4887-972f-57e24b100c01/17720.jpg)

Great moment where CM Punk FINALLY tags AJ Lee into this match and the crowd EXPLODES.

But the ref didn't see it

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/d0c84bf7-ec9d-45e9-8e06-f371b2c675b0/17728.jpg)

AJ Lee officially enters the ring for the first time in over a decade

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/94ae48d7-9a17-46c8-b89d-57ae7c13d8e5/17731.jpg)

Husband and Wife submissions and shining wizards from CM Punk and AJ Lee

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/5f31a09f-584b-48d8-bd3c-d02dd5e04f28/17734.jpg)

Husband and Wife Pedigrees from Rollins and Becky Lynch!!

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/6bc691b5-8d25-401f-bdcf-b3d020df8f55/17743.jpg)

AJ Lee taps out Becky Lynch to win the match.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/923a150a-a2b0-4425-b83b-c11c5988bced/17746.jpg)

Stephanie McMahon is the first inductee in the 2026 WWE Hall of Fame Class

The Undertaker makes a surprise appearance. He drives his bike over to Stephanie McMahon and Nick Khan.

He takes a seat next to Stephanie. He asks are you ready?

Then he surprised her with the announcement.

* * *

![](https://images.squarespace-cdn.com/content/v1/5d56e145f80b7500016ba502/2ca8968f-cee2-412b-a67a-824e1dcc20c9/17753.jpg)

The referee just cost Drew McIntyre the WWE Championship.

*   ## **_WWE Championship: Cody Rhodes def. Drew McIntyre_**
    

Drew McIntyre was going to Claymore Cody through the announce table bottom again, but the referee stood in front of him.

Drew finally moved the ref but it was too late. He crashes through by himself and is damaged.

He tries to hit a Claymore but he's too hurt. Cody hits the Cody Cutter and a Cross Rhodes for the win.